MITS:Identification.MITS:StructureDescription: Welcome to Park Place at Van Dorn, Inside our beautiful homes you'll discover no detail was overlooked as we offer great amenities such as nine foot ceilings with crown molding, garden soaking tubs, contemporary white-on-white kitchens and spacious closets. Personalized options such as lofts, attached and detached garages, as well as optional storage, help make every home a perfect fit. Our clubhouse hosts a Cyber Cafe, where you can gather to enjoy a cup of coffee or surf the web. Park Place at Van Dorn is also proud to offer a courtesy shuttle to the Van Dorn metro station, and a cardio theater accessible 24 hours a day. With all these amenities and more, we're sure you'll agree that Park Place at Van Dorn is the place you'll love to call home! Welcome to the lifestyle you have earned!
